---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>raediy</title>
    <meta name="description" content="静かな下準備だけが進んでいます。" />
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: dark;
        font-family: "Inter", "Hiragino Sans", "Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN", "Noto Sans JP", sans-serif;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at 18% 22%, rgba(144, 96, 55, 0.16), transparent 55%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 78% 18%, rgba(92, 65, 42, 0.18), transparent 58%),
          linear-gradient(140deg, #1e120b, #3a2314 52%, #1b0f08);
        color: rgba(248, 236, 222, 0.82);
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      main {
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 4rem 1.5rem 3.5rem;
      }

      .shell {
        max-width: 48rem;
        width: 100%;
        display: grid;
        gap: 2.25rem;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.75rem);
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        text-transform: lowercase;
        margin: 0;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 1rem;
      }

      h1 span {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        width: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 3.75rem);
        aspect-ratio: 1;
        border-radius: 18%;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(146, 94, 58, 0.55), rgba(203, 147, 94, 0.35));
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 235, 210, 0.12);
        box-shadow: 0 14px 38px rgba(30, 16, 7, 0.55);
        position: relative;
      }

      h1 span::before,
      h1 span::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 235, 210, 0.3);
      }

      h1 span::before {
        inset: 18%;
        opacity: 0.7;
      }

      h1 span::after {
        inset: 32%;
        opacity: 0.4;
      }

      h1 strong {
        font-weight: inherit;
      }

      h1 em {
        font-style: normal;
        font-weight: inherit;
        color: rgba(244, 222, 197, 0.65);
        letter-spacing: 0.34em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        font-size: clamp(0.7rem, 1.2vw, 0.9rem);
      }

      p {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: rgba(245, 231, 214, 0.8);
      }

      .whisper {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 2.1vw, 1.35rem);
        line-height: 1.85;
        color: rgba(249, 233, 212, 0.88);
        max-width: 36rem;
      }

      footer {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        padding: 0 1.5rem 1.5rem;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        color: rgba(231, 210, 188, 0.46);
      }

      footer span {
        position: relative;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
      }

      footer svg {
        width: 0.75rem;
        height: 0.75rem;
        opacity: 0.45;
      }

      .trace {
        position: relative;
      }

      .trace a {
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        opacity: 0;
        text-indent: -9999px;
      }

      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        main {
          padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem 2.75rem;
        }

        .shell {
          gap: 2rem;
        }

        h1 {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
        }

        h1 span {
          margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
        }

        h1 em {
          letter-spacing: 0.28em;
        }
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        main {
          padding: 3.25rem 1.25rem 2.5rem;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <div class="shell">
        <h1>
          <span aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <strong>raediy</strong>
          <em>in preparation</em>
        </h1>
        <p class="whisper">
          すべての責任ある人々のため、手元で息づく新しいカラクリが
          静かに鼓動しています。
        </p>
      </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
      <div class="trace">
        <span>
          © {currentYear} raediy
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.7" />
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.14" />
          </svg>
        </span>
        <a href="https://admin.raediy.com" aria-label="administrator"></a>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
